text: Tihao Chiang is an electrical engineer working for Ambarella Taiwan, Ltd., in Hsinchu, Taiwan. Chiang was named a Fellow of the Institute of Electrical and Electronics Engineers (IEEE) in 2014 for his contributions to the theory and applications of video coding algorithms. == References == Category:Fellow Members of the IEEE Category:Living people Category:Taiwanese electrical engineers Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
